group__inner-container\">\n<p>There&#x2019;s no doubt that this is the heart of the city, lively at any time of the day or night. Enjoy a port while you overlook the river and the majestic Dom Luis I bridge, before exploring the charming hillside streets.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Don&#x2019;t miss the Praca da Ribeira square: one of the oldest and most famous squares in Porto.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square.jpg\" alt=\"porto city trip Praca da Ribeira square\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"288\" alt=\"porto city trip Praca da Ribeira square\" class=\"wp-image-48423 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-300x192.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-600x384.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-800x513.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-1080x692.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-450x288.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-1536x984.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-30x19.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-163x104.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-281x180.jpg 281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-768x492.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-1024x656.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-1440x923.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square-30x19.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105202\/porto-city-trip-Praca-da-Ribeira-square.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-2-escada-guindais\">2. <strong>Escada Guindais<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Porto&#x2019;s hilly scenery means there are plenty of steep climbs and amazing views to be found. Street stairs are a common find, and the Escada Guindais is the main stairway leading away from the Ribeira neighborhood. Walk up the stairs and admire all the old-fashioned houses, watching the locals as they hang out their washing. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/porto-all\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Porto.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n\n<a class=\"block-googlemaps\" title=\"Get our Google Maps Legend\" data-maptype=\"Portugal \" href=\"\/shop\/google-maps\/portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            <div class=\"block-googlemaps__container\">\n                <div class=\"block-googlemaps__content\">\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__title\">Our Portugal  tips in your Google Maps?<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__text\">We made it easier for you! All our tips: favourite to do's, restaurants, hikes, secret spots &amp; more in Google Maps!<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__button\">Shop our Maps <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__notice\" style=\"display:none; font-size:12px; margin-top:15px;\">The map for this destination will be available soon. Thank you for your interest!<\/span>\n                <\/div>\n                <img class=\"block-googlemaps__image lazyload\" tempsrc=\"\/build\/images\/google-maps-banner-image.png\" alt=\"google maps phone\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n\n\n<fi