                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/47676&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105142\/porto-portugal-best-things-to-do-1.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105142\/porto-portugal-best-things-to-do-1-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105142\/porto-portugal-best-things-to-do-1-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"10 Great Things To Do in Porto, Portugal\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-3-porto-cathedral\">3. <strong>Porto Cathedral<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Set in the middle of a huge open square, the Porto Cathedral symbolizes the city. Although its stone facade is impressive, its beauty really happens on the inside! <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/porto-all\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Porto.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105253\/porto-portugal-city-trip-best-things-to-do.jpg\" alt=\"porto portugal city trip best things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"264\" height=\"338\" alt=\"porto portugal city trip best things to do\" class=\"wp-image-48366 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1502px) 100vw, 1502px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105253\/porto-portugal-city-trip-best-things-to-do.jpg 1502w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105253\/porto-portugal-city-trip-best-things-to-do-300x383.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105253\/porto-portugal-city-trip-best-things-to-do-600x767.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105253\/porto-portugal-city-trip-best-things-to-do-469x600.jpg 469w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105253\/porto-portugal-city-trip-best-things-to-do-634x810.jpg 634w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105253\/porto-portugal-city-trip-best-things-to-do-264x338.jpg 264w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105253\/porto-portugal-city-trip-best-things-to-do-1202x1536.jpg 1202w, https:\/\/st