lass=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105219\/porto-Sao-Bento-Station.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-8-livraria-lello-top-thing-to-do-in-porto\">8. Livraria Lello &#x2013; Top Thing To Do in Porto<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Immerse yourself in the magical world of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/livraria-lello-porto\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Livraria Lello: a stunning bookstore<\/a> made famous from JK Rowling&#x2019;s Harry Potter stories. The story goes that when JK Rowling used to live in Porto, the bookstore became the inspiration for her novels. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>More about:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/livraria-lello-porto\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Livraria Lello Bookstore<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105340\/porto-portugal-things-to-do-Livraria-Lello-bookstore-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"porto portugal things to do Livraria Lello bookstore\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"porto portugal things to do Livraria 