oy an hour or two wandering through the luxurious rooms at the end of your second day in Porto.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Price:<\/strong> 10 EUR. <strong>Opening times<\/strong>: 9.30 AM to 6.30 PM. In the winter months November to March 9.30 AM-1 PM \/ 2 PM-5.30 PM<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> on your way, stop off at the Igreja dos Clerigos: an impressive baroque church with a huge bell tower, which can be seen from all over the city. Climb the bell tower for awesome views across Porto! Ticket prices and opening times can be found <a href=\"http:\/\/www.torredosclerigos.pt\/pt\/bilheteira\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">here<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore\">\n<div class=\"block-link__container\">\n<p><strong>Get to know:<\/strong>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/sintra-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The fairytale palaces and castles of Sintra<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city.jpg\" alt=\"porto portugal city\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"315\" alt=\"porto portugal city\" class=\"wp-image-48154 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-300x210.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-600x420.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-800x560.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-1080x757.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-450x315.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-1536x1076.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-163x114.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-257x180.jpg 257w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-768x538.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-1024x717.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/23105324\/porto-portugal-city-1440x1009.jpg 1440w\" tempsrc=\"https: