w.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/lisbon-citytrip\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Lisbon<\/a>. From Lisbon, it&#x2019;s a <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/train\/lisbon\/porto\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">direct train to Porto<\/a> that takes around 3 hours.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/rent-car-portugal\/\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Rent a car in Portugal<\/a> through <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. Free cancellation up to 1 hour before rental start and all insurance is included (so no surprises when you pick up your car). <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105155\/porto-portugal-city-guide.jpg\" alt=\"porto portugal city guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"porto portugal city guide\" class=\"wp-image-48432 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105155\/porto-portugal-city-guide.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourh