-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-around\">Getting Around<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#x2019;re in Porto, the city is small and all the sights can be walked to. The city is very hilly, so wear good shoes, and buy a pass for the trams and funicular railway if you get tired. Alternatively, you can use Uber to get around quickly and easily.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/best-places-to-visit-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best Places to visit in Portugal<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105152\/portugal-tram-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"portugal tram\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"portugal tram\" class=\"wp-image-48433 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105152\/portugal-tram-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105152\/portugal-tram-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105152\/portugal-tram-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23105152\/portugal-tram-400x600.jpg 400w, htt